	2 of "restauration rapide" endof
	3 of "courriel" endof
	4 of "selfies" endof
	5 of "nouvelles de celebrites" endof
	6 of "videos virales" endof
	7 of "streamers de jeux video" endof
	8 of "le concept dhygiene" endof
	9 of "fanfiction grossierement illustree" endof
	10 of "chan" endof
	11 of "creepypasta" endof
	endcase ;

	: one-line1 "Tout ira bien si je peux me rendre au Canada." ;
